{"tid":1112168,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"契妹唐詩詠首開腔","createTime":"2019-04-17T09:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T01:58:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4049d87e3f38b749ff7bf3faf413caae641ab8","tid":1112168,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/photo/bkn-20190417150120136-0417_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190417153521\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190417%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190417150120136-0417_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190417153521&h=27e9b275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人馬國明女友黃心穎被爆介入許志安夫婦之間的感情，他至今仍未開腔回應，但網民一致替他感到不值，直指他遇人不淑！而身為馬國明契妹、被外界公認與馬國明合襯的唐詩詠亦於社交網開腔，意有所指表示：「It is not impermanence that makes us suffer. What makes us suffer is wanting things to be permanent when they are not.（使我們受苦的不是無常，而是當我們想把一件非永恒的事情變成永恒。）」更標籤：「人生無常、當下最真、love and compassion（愛與同情）」不過配圖就是她在法國巴黎聖母院前的照片，未知是否因該建築近日發生大火嚴重損毀而有感而發。<br />\n<br />\n但網民見她發文都紛紛起哄並留言，表示：「你一早同馬國明一齊就好啦！」、「快點去安慰馬國明！」、「你們好襯，馬國明咁好仔，真係要安慰吓佢。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/bkn-20190417150120136-0417_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190417%2Fbkn-20190417150120136-0417_00862_001.html&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAryWBhM8hN5wqk8YifI4Fu34%3D&h=40d7b774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190417/bkn-20190417150120136-0417_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"84f341d62a93bd46b9022661eecde634c5ec4128","tid":1112168,"uid":40470,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:32:26.000Z","msg":"關佢撚事咩<br />\n<br />\n呀豬呀狗都開腔"},{"pid":"09ad648256c36f24cfc2b81bc45aee4ed187360b","tid":1112168,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T09:35:33.000Z","msg":"唐姨名正言順出手<img src=\"/ass